business.name:
Reeds in the Desert Oasis
(Major of Conscription)

business.note:
Firbolg Naturists believe that firbolgs are creatures of nature that should be left alone, as they are part of nature itself. They help to preserve the natural balance. As a result they should be under Astorrel jurisdiction.

Firbolg Inclusivits believe that firbolgs are intelligent, sentient creatures that fall under the purview of the Kingdom of Astor. As a result they should be under the jurisdiction of the Astornox, including magicborn conscription.
